Each device has its lifespan - some devices use higher quality components than others and can last years. However, repeated use or accidents can cause issues that require professional MacBook repair technicians.

12"" MacBook A1534 Water Damage Repair

Have you spilled a drink on your original 12"" Macbook A1534, maybe water from the sink, or worse a toilet? Maybe you accidentally washed it? Believe it or not your Macbook can be saved from water damage. We have over a 90% success rate of saving water damaged laptops, regardless of what was spilled on it. You have come to the right place if you're searching for a reliable company to perform macbook water damage repair.
We’ve seen it all from swimming pools to port-o-potty’s
column2: send us your water damaged device and let us see what our skilled repair staff can do to save your device.

column1: MacBook Water Damage Tips:

If your laptop has suffered water damage, don't turn it on, don't hit any buttons, or try to charge it. Just dry it off as best you can and send it to us right away. Make sure when ordering your repair, that you select the correct Macbook model.

We know how important your laptop is to you, so we will send you an email when your laptop is finished being repaired and is shipping back to you.
